agents.fld_userDetails_Claim: Lorel is a native Texan and has been working in the Real Estate industry in Houston for over 18 years assisting buyers and sellers in all their real estate needs. Lorel knows the areas, schools and the importance of customer service and integrity. Lorel owned and operated her own successful wholesale & Couture Fashion Design Company in New York and abroad for many years providing 1st class service to her clients. Lorel is well traveled and has lived in Dubai, Saudi Arabia, Switzerland, Holland, Italy & New York. While living in Dubai she received her Real Estate License and enjoyed assisting her International high end clients specializing in residential new construction. Lorel is a Certified Dr. Sears Wellness Coach & a Master Reiki Healer. Lorels international travels, marketing knowledge, savvy business skills, & customer service experience gives her the cutting edge and has attributed to her success in the real estate industry. Her passion is making sure her clients are happy and needs are met and insuring their satisfaction is top priority. Lorel is also a member of Unity Church and involved with Unity Pets to promote love and kindness to animals and raising money for various animal shelters in the Houston areas. Lorel also volunteers at Make A Wish Foundation that assists kids with life threatening diseases. Lorel understands the stress of moving and enjoys assisting her clients in finding their dream home and always puts her clients needs first ensuring that their move will be a pleasant and stress free experience.
